Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Habit Burger
Description: A great burger joint in the middle of downtown Santa Barbara. Within walking distance from bothe the art museum and the warf.
ImageURL: http://www.habitburger.com/wp-content/uploads/habitburger-logo.jpg (I couldn't find a picture of the establishment, but its on State street and is in a small alley)

Name: McCallum Theater
Description: The McCallum is a very large theatre from where I used to live. It hosts a vast array of production ranging from musical events to theatrical plays.

Name: Palm Desert Aquatic Center
Description: This was the pool that I worked at before I came here. It was a large facility with waterslides and diving boards. Most of the local highschools would compete in tournaments and swim meets here.

Name: Catalina Island
Description: I went to several amazing camps here when I was younger. It was truly a wonderful experince to come to this beautiful desert island.

Name: University of Kansas
Description: This is the college that my family gre up around. A lot of my family have gone there and its where I grew up. I remeber hearing so many stories of the sprawling hill the campus is on and the towering campanel at the center.
